Spent the morning in the chair with @carydeuber at @lemmonavenue & I’m already feeling a million times more confident! She’s an artist when it comes to helping me look & feel my best, and I am grateful to have an injector (& dear friend) who I trust to decide what my skin needs! 

Here’s what she did today:
-Neurotoxin throughout the top of my forehead, crows feet, 11’s, bunny lines, chin (the dreaded dimpled “orange peel” chin lol), and along my platysmal bands in my neck, which helps with crepey skin and sagging. 
-For facial balancing along my jawline, she used Volux XC filler, which is a hyaluronic acid injectable gel for deep injection to improve moderate to severe loss of jawline definition. 
-In the past she has used Hyperdilute Radiesse to make my neck build elastin & collagen, and I have also had a Halo laser treatment @theresadoeslasers! 

*Remember every patient is different….with unique skin and varying goals, so you need a consultation with an injector you trust! Cary recommends to ask for “Facial balancing with jawline filler” if you are wanting results like mine, and let them give you their best recommendation based on what is best for your unique case!
